      "content": "it’s just so exhausting. trying to pretend like i'm still a person when i'm just... gone inside. i look at the sun coming up and i just feel this intense dread because it means i have to participate in a world that doesn't even matter to me anymore. why am i even fighting it? it feels like i'm just dragging a heavy weight around for no reason.",
